graph LR
    RHODSOp[RHODS Operator<br/>OpenDataHub Operator]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    RHODSOp -->|orchestration<br/>platform| K8s[Kubernetes 1.24+<br/>REQUIRED]
    RHODSOp -->|enterprise<br/>distribution| OpenShift[OpenShift 4.12+<br/>REQUIRED for RHOAI]
    RHODSOp -->|webhook TLS<br/>certificates| CertMgr[Cert Manager /<br/>OpenShift Service CA<br/>REQUIRED]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional)
    RHODSOp -.->|monitoring<br/>infrastructure| PromOp[Prometheus Operator<br/>v0.68+<br/>OPTIONAL]
    RHODSOp -.->|service mesh<br/>for model serving| Istio[Istio /<br/>Service Mesh 2.4+<br/>OPTIONAL]
    RHODSOp -.->|serverless<br/>model serving| Serverless[OpenShift Serverless<br/>Knative 1.30+<br/>OPTIONAL]
    RHODSOp -.->|observability<br/>platform| RHOBS[RHOBS Monitoring<br/>OPTIONAL for RHOAI]

    %% Internal ODH/RHOAI Components (Deployed by Operator)
    RHODSOp -->|deploys| Dashboard[ODH Dashboard<br/>Web UI]
    RHODSOp -->|deploys| KServeOp[KServe Operator<br/>Model Serving]
    RHODSOp -->|deploys| Pipelines[Kubeflow Pipelines<br/>ML Orchestration]
    RHODSOp -->|deploys| ModelReg[Model Registry Operator<br/>Model Metadata]
    RHODSOp -->|deploys| NotebookCtrl[Notebook Controller<br/>Jupyter Lifecycle]
    RHODSOp -->|deploys| RayOp[Ray Operator<br/>Distributed Computing]
    RHODSOp -->|deploys| TrainingOp[Training Operator<br/>Distributed Training]
    RHODSOp -->|deploys| Kueue[Kueue<br/>Job Queueing]
    RHODSOp -->|deploys| TrustyAI[TrustyAI<br/>AI Explainability]
    RHODSOp -->|deploys| FeastOp[Feast Operator<br/>Feature Store]
    RHODSOp -->|deploys| MLflowOp[MLflow Operator<br/>Tracking Server]
    RHODSOp -->|deploys| MaaS[ModelsAsService<br/>Managed Serving API]

    %% Infrastructure Services (Managed by Operator)
    RHODSOp -->|configures| Monitoring[Monitoring Service<br/>Prometheus/AlertManager/Grafana]
    RHODSOp -->|configures| Auth[Auth Service<br/>Authentication/Authorization]
    RHODSOp -->|configures| Gateway[Gateway Config<br/>API Gateway]

    %% External Services (Egress)
    RHODSOp -->|pulls images| Registry[Container Registries<br/>443/TCP HTTPS]
    RHODSOp -->|user auth| OAuth[OpenShift OAuth<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS]

    %% Integration Points (Components integrate with operator)
    Dashboard -.->|UI management| RHODSOp
    Pipelines -.->|auto deploy models| KServeOp
    KServeOp -.->|model metadata| ModelReg

    %% Shared Infrastructure
    KServeOp -.->|uses| Istio
    KServeOp -.->|uses| Serverless
    Monitoring -->|scrapes| RHODSOp

    %% Styling
    style RHODSOp fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:4px,color:#fff

    %% External Required Dependencies
    style K8s fill:#326ce5,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
